SUMMARY:Karaoke After-Party!
DESCRIPTION:Stick around after the show and take over the stage with our Karaoke Party!\nPick your stage name and sign up. It’s free and easy\, with over 58\,000 songs spanning a century of all genres.\nKaraoke sign-ups at 10:00 pm\, and karaoke begins at 10:30pm.\nThis is an inclusive\, welcoming environment with a friendly\, positive crowd. We love to cheer for first-timers and crooning veterans. Time to pick out that duet with your bestie\, grab your air guitar\, and come party.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/karaoke-after-party-2/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Recreation
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Karaoke-300x.png
