SUMMARY:Fresh Takes: True West Student Film Festival
DESCRIPTION:True West Film Center presents Fresh Takes\, the True West Student Film Festival\, a one-day showcase celebrating emerging filmmakers from the Sonoma County region. Featuring original short films produced by local elementary and high school students\, the festival line up reflects the creativity\, diversity\, and individual voices of the next generation. Held at the new True West Cinemas in downtown Healdsburg\, the festival will present selected films on the big screen before a theatrical audience and award a variety of prizes. Fresh Takes is presented in collaboration with the Sonoma County Office of Education.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/fresh-takes-true-west-student-film-festival/
LOCATION:True West Cinemas\, 371 Healdsburg Ave\, Healdsburg\, 95448
CATEGORIES:Film
END:VEVENT
