SUMMARY:Park Rx—Yoga Hikes 2026
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy your yoga experience in the beautiful setting of our park! Susan Topf’s Yoga Hike balances a mix of easy hiking and gentle yoga postures\, breath work and guided meditation\, no mat necessary. The route varies on weather conditions and group interest\, typically covering 2-3 miles of varied terrain. All levels and ages welcome. \nTickets are $20. Please wear weather-appropriate clothing to feel comfortable being in a natural setting and bring water (as needed). Meet outside the Visitor Center unless otherwise noted in the reminder email prior to the hike. Limited to 12 participants. \nSonoma County Resident? Free with a November 2025 or newer Park Rx from a participating Sonoma County Medical Provider.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/park-rx-yoga-hikes-2026-4/
LOCATION:CA
CATEGORIES:Recreation
END:VEVENT
