SUMMARY:The Social Contractors at Murphy's
DESCRIPTION:Founded by Jason E. Davies on the heels of the pandemic\, The Social Contractors offer an upbeat blend of melodic original rock and classic hits you know and love.\nJason’s tightly crafted tunes feature improvised solos with pointed lyrics that span edgy political and environmental themes to tales of unrequited love and introspection – all with an ultimately optimistic perspective on the possible. In addition to Jason on guitar and vocals\, The Social Contractors include Rob Neidel on bass and vocals\, Travis Thayer on keyboard and saxophone\, and Chris Oatman on drums. Alternate members include Dan Ellecamp\, Nick Schneider\, and Scott McKenzie on drums\, and Alex Fabian-Davies on bass.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-social-contractors-at-murphys-3/
LOCATION:Murphy’s Irish Pub & Restaurant\, 464 1st St E.\, Sonoma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.2924023;-122.4558064
