SUMMARY:Corned Beef & Cabbage Feed
DESCRIPTION:Join the shenanigans and enjoy tasty food to benefit Penngrove community projects.\nSaturday\, March 14\, 2026\n3:00 p.m. – 7:00 p.m.\nPenngrove Clubhouse\, 385 Woodward Ave.\, Penngrove\, CA \nMenu: corned beef\, cabbage\, potatoes\, and carrots cooked by the volunteer kitchen crew. No-host bar. \nDine in or take it to To-Go. \nBring cash to support Penngrove 4-H with your purchases from the dessert table. \nTickets are at Odd Cookie Bakery in Penngrove\, or online at https://corned@eventbrite.com \nThe cost is $30 general admission or $10 for children under 12. Children’s tickets are available at the door. \nAll proceeds help maintain Penngrove Social Firemen’s Clubhouse and Penngrove Park\, for the benefit of the community. The PSF is a non-profit 501 (c) (3). For information\, call 707 318-2191 or see www.penngrovesocialfiremen.org
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/corned-beef-cabbage-feed/
LOCATION:Penngrove Community Clubhouse\, 385 Woodward Ave.\, Penngrove\, CA
CATEGORIES:Holiday
GEO:38.29754165;-122.66543807383476
