SUMMARY:Jeremy Gorman at Adobe Road Winery
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Adobe Road Winery in downtown Petaluma. Sip on award-winning wines while enjoying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose from wines by the glass or bottle to discover new favorites. Reserve your spot on Tock and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine wine\, and good company! \nAbout Jeremy Gorman\nFor San Francisco Bay Area multi-instrumentalist\, Jeremy Gorman\, music has been nothing short of a lifetime journey of self-expression and self-realization. Currently performing as a solo artist\, Jeremy has collaborated with many bands around the North Bay area\, including a project titled spaceMüs with daughter\, Blair Gorman. \nWith a deep knowledge of music theory\, along with a vast range of musical tastes\, Jeremy creates story-driven songs that capture ideas of hope and gratitude\, and of his own personal life’s journey.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/jeremy-gorman-at-adobe-road-winery-3/
LOCATION:Adobe Road Winery\, 6 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.234020;-122.639530
