SUMMARY:FLAMENCO! LIVE! Saturday\, March 14 at The Big Easy Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an intoxicating evening of fiery flamenco performances when FLAMENCO! LIVE! sets the stage on fire with the fury and passion of Spain’s legendary Gypsies (Roma) with a\nFlamenco Dinner Show in the intimate atmosphere of THE BIG EASY. EXPERIENCE flamenco as stirring dances\, blazing guitars\, and soulful singing will transport you to another place and time.\nFEEL the HEAT… \nFLAMENCO!\nLIVE! \nSaturday\, March 14th\n2026 \nMelissa Cruz ~ Dancer\nBAOBOB Flamenco Dancers:\nMaria Soledad Sanchez\, Kendra Pearson and Yumi Dews\nPirouz “De Caspio” ~ Singer\nRoberto Aguilar ~ Guitarist \nShowtime: 6 pm\nDoors: 5 pm\n$25\nPay at the Door\nCash or Card \nat\nThe Big Easy\nClub and Restaurant\n128 American Alley\nPetaluma USA\n*****************************************\nFlamenco Shows every other Month!\nThe 2nd Saturday of the Month.\nAlways different Artists.\nAlways a different Show. \nFlamenco Dinner Show with delicious food and a Full Bar are available\, not included in entrance fee.\nArrive early\, get a good table and enjoy the food!\nLine forms at 4:45 pm \n*Limited Reservations available for parties of 5 – 6 or more.\nCall at:\n(707) 774- 9072 \n*Large fully ventilated restaurant\, plenty of room for spacing\, masks optional. \nFLAMENCO! LIVE! was envisioned\, conceived\, and has thrived since 2002 in Sonoma County\, California\, now celebrating 24 years! Presenting the collaborative efforts of the Bay Area’s finest Flamenco Singers\, Guitarists and Dancers\, and supporting local Flamenco students\, dreamers\, and talents\, our goal has been to present top-notch performances. Phoebe Vernier “La Fibi” has brought decades of artistry and energy to the public of Sonoma County for the purpose of sharing the music\, song and dance\, the treasure of Southern Spain. Whether in the formal theater or in a casual setting\, the respect\, purity\, and integrity of this traditional\, yet living and evolving art form is always foremost. \nNow in our 4rd Year of fiery Flamenco Shows! \n“Best Performing Dance Company” – The Northbay Bohemian’s\nBEST of the Northbay!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/flamenco-live-saturday-march-14-at-the-big-easy-petaluma/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Dance Performance,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Flamenco-live-Mar-26.jpg
GEO:38.2346;-122.641
