SUMMARY:Caltucky at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for an upbeat evening of driving strings\, tight harmonies\, and back-porch energy under the redwoods. Caltucky Bluegrass Band brings a fresh\, high-spirited take on bluegrass — blending traditional roots with a California-grown edge for a show that’s equal parts barn-burner and feel-good hang. \nCaltucky Bluegrass Band is a roots-forward string band with a sound that lives at the crossroads of classic bluegrass tradition and West Coast swagger. Built on fast\, clean instrumentation and a deep love for American roots music\, the band delivers a set that moves effortlessly between hard-driving standards\, sing-along favorites\, and fresh interpretations that feel both familiar and new.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/caltucky-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
