SUMMARY:VOSR Annual Crab Feed Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:Victory Outreach Santa Rosa is dedicated to serving at-risk youth through weekly mentorship and leadership programs\, supporting low-income families with consistent children and family services\, operating a free residential men’s rehabilitation home\, and hosting outreach events throughout the year for individuals coming out of incarceration and those battling drug addiction. Through these initiatives\, we work to restore hope\, strengthen families\, and transform lives. \nTo help expand and strengthen these vital programs\, we are hosting our annual Crab Feed Fundraiser\, which brings together community leaders\, families\, and supporters for an evening with a purpose. \nENJOY A GREAT NIGHT FULL OF FOOD AND FUN WHILE MAKING A LASTING IMPACT IN OUR COMMUNITY!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/vosr-annual-crab-feed-fundraiser/
LOCATION:Victory Outreach Santa Rosa Church\, 4042 Sebastopol Rd.\, Santa Rosa\, 95407
CATEGORIES:Other
END:VEVENT
